[barman]
; Generic barman buy multipliers.
; He runs a bar, not an arms store. Food, drink, smokes — that's his economy.
; Mutant meat is his best buy: the cook needs a steady supply.
; Zone items (artifacts) are accepted — barmans fence these as a side business.
; Everything weapon or gear related is simply not his problem.
; Normalized to 1.0 max. General trader_discount applied separately.

